Conclusion
To conclude, the survey highlights landscape of software and hardware tools used for cybercrime investigations. It showcases many advanced and sophisticated tools to ease investigations. It can also be observed that co-operation and integrity between various software and hardware tools enhances cybercrime investigations. Finally, there is a need to ensure that all the tools being used should be up to date and modern and ethical aspect to use such tools should not be neglected. All in all, both kind of cybercrime investigation tools enhance security and increase combat response to cyber threats.
